de.uniheidelberg.cl.swp.datastructure
Class Feature<e>

java.lang.Object
  de.uniheidelberg.cl.swp.datastructure.Feature<e>
Type Parameters:
e - The type of a feature (e.g. Boolean, Integer, String, ...).
public class Feature<e>
extends java.lang.Object

A generic feature which is extracet by AbstractFeatureExtractor. The implementing feature extractor (such as FE_distance) knows the generic type of the feature and deals with it appropriately.
